description: This is the post-apocalypse era, where the resources on earth have been wiped out. Humans created brain-sucking machines to absorb memories and knowledge in the brain and process them to revive electric power. Now, the contents of the brain are used as a means of buying and selling transactions. But the more often the machine is used, more stupid and unethical humans will be. 1000 AI generated NFT collectible
